संरक्षण नीति

van sanrkchan ki Neeti hamare Desh ke liye koi nai baat nahi hai .hum aaj taut par is baat ki nahi jante ki van hamare Desh me kuch Manav prajatiyo ke avas bhi hai Bharat ke kuch jagaho samudae sarkari karmchariyo ki sahayta se aapne Savas sathani ke sanrkchan me Lage hua hai kyuki isi se Baad me unki jarorat Pori ho Sakti hai Sariska bagh reserve me Rajasthan ke logo ne van sanrkchan adhiniyam ke tahat vaha se khanan kam band kar vane ke liye aaj bhi Sangharsh kar rahe hai kai jagaha par to khud bhi van jivo ke Savas ki raksha kar rahe hai.